<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-3397] Cleanup Test TokenStreams so they are reusable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3397</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Many TokenStreams created in tests are not reusable.  Some do some really messy things which prevent their reuse so we may have to change the tests themselves.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We&apos;ll target back porting this to 3x.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
